title: 820-3437 rotates the cooler, but does not turn on
message:
This mac arrived with various oxidations close to the u1900, u6100, Y1915, Q8150 and components nearby. Replaces the oxidized ones and checked the tensions. The mac turns on the cooler, but it has no image and has no data reading on the USB's.

Voltage: PPbus_g3h 8.59V; PP3V42_G3H 3.42v; PP5V_s0 5.12V; ALL_SYS_PWRGD 3.3V; PM_SLP_Sx_L 3.30V;

Coils;
L7430 1.2v
L7630 1.07v
L7310 1.71v
L7320 1.71v

This mac is return, the first time was placed the serial number in the BIOS, because it was without s / n.

title: 820-3437 rotates the cooler, but does not turn on
message:
Try known good BIOS first.
You should have some clean file for this board.

PLT_RESET_L is high?
Check all SPI Bus Series Termination resistors and their traces.
